Subject: [PATCH 0/3] platform/x86: msi-wmi-platform: add MS-16V5 (GS66 12Ux) support

Adds MSI MS-16V5 (Stealth GS66 12UHS and siblings) support to the
in-review msi-wmi-platform fan-curve/platform_profile/charge series, plus
two general improvements found while enabling it.

Tested on a GS66 12UHS (EC 16V5EMS1.108): hwmon fan RPM + pwm1/pwm2 fan
curves (CPU/GPU), platform_profile (EC shift-mode 0xD2) and battery charge
threshold (EC 0xD7) all work; charge stop + start=end-10 hysteresis and the
resume re-apply were verified on hardware.

Patch 1 adds the board quirk. Patch 2 fixes a general suspend/resume issue
(the EC drops shift-mode across suspend and the firmware does not restore
it). Patch 3 lets a board family be matched by its 4-char EC firmware ID
instead of enumerating every DMI board name.

Note: based on the in-review fan-curve/profile/tdp/battery series and needs
rebasing onto its current revision before submission; TDP (PLx) left unset
for MS-16V5 pending validated limits.

Developed with AI assistance per Documentation/process/coding-assistants.rst
(see Assisted-by trailers). The submitter has reviewed the changes and takes
responsibility per the Signed-off-by.


Florian (1):
  platform/x86: msi-wmi-platform: add MS-16V5 (Stealth GS66 12Ux) quirk

dev (2):
